                "text": "A satyr\u2019s wineskin magically enchants any alcohol inside. With an Interact action, a living creature can imbibe the alcohol and gain a +1 item bonus to Will saves and a +3 item bonus to Will saves against fear effects for the following hour. When the wineskin is removed from a satyr\u2019s person, the magic remains only until the wine spoils. The wineskin holds up to eight drafts of wine."
